title: Celebrate the 3rd Anniversary of the Disney Festival of Fantasy Parade with Disney PhotoPass Service
text:
Three years ago today the Disney Festival of Fantasy Parade first came alive at Magic Kingdom Park !
I could write countless paragraphs about how much I adore this dazzling parade (the Tangled float is my favorite!), but instead, I’ll just let you appreciate the spectacular pageantry for yourself. Enjoy this video of parade highlights below, presented by Disney PhotoPass Service .
Away we go, it’s a Festival of Fantasy!
